{"tid":1156484,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"被問「如果我們死了會怎樣」奇洛李維斯答：「愛我們的人，會很想念我們的」","createTime":"2019-05-15T15:38:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-17T03:24:24.000Z","uid":41343,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"460e151c6d34f6480e02cc61d34436dc4eaf9841","tid":1156484,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T15:38:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/oNu6NyMkp8k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FoNu6NyMkp8k&d=ljHbDMTA27iaUnmVhJlU2NHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=3273330a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/oNu6NyMkp8k</a><br />\n9：50<br />\n<br />\n主持諗住攪下gag<br />\n結果男神俾個咁嘅答案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n奇洛：電影叫做《阿比與阿弟與音樂 ( Bill &amp; Ted Face the Music，暫譯）》他們發現自己必須在很短的時間，像是80分鐘之類的時間內寫一首歌，而且不只是為了要拯救這個世界，還必須是為了整個宇宙而寫，寫不出來的話，就是整個宇宙的終結了。<br />\n<br />\n主持人：所以也就是說，不只是自己的死亡，而是一切存在的死亡......奇洛，你覺得如果我們死了，會發生什麼事？<br />\n<br />\n「......我知道那些愛我們的人，會很想念我們的」"},{"pid":"bddd57d01c97ec8427649f42802bfdf41140484e","tid":1156484,"uid":136662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T15:40:20.000Z","msg":"然而奇神已看透死神的玩笑"},{"pid":"c160f778231b43ace1e3ccc5095d7196c1a3bb37","tid":1156484,"uid":92459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T15:46:12.000Z","msg":"屈機"},{"pid":"2183449058ce4bdcbe3837b260519d681d1cbbe9","tid":1156484,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T15:47:42.000Z","msg":"勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d256098049c58de880d37cb5eb6a7075520c640","tid":1156484,"uid":41343,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"bddd57d01c97ec8427649f42802bfdf41140484e","tid":1156484,"uid":136662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,